{"tid":1614182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"3/10 [開盤] 港鐵正檢查各車站損毀情況，部分車站或設施或未能於早上恢復服務","createTime":"2019-10-02T17:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T01:04:44.000Z","uid":89,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"69aa56b40092873a4baf481bebdadca6ca952081","tid":1614182,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:09:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">賭幾多聽朝實站站開得返</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日都話聽朝未能恢復嚇港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日都狼來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，晚上多個重鐵及輕鐵車站設施被示威者蓄意破壞和縱火，令致乘客、員工及鐵路安全受到嚴重影響，予以強烈譴責，並已就有關案件報警。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵人員現正檢查各車站情況，工程人員需要評估損毀程度，並會盡力復修以維持對市民的服務。部分車站或設施有機會未能在明天恢復提供服務。<br />\n<br />\n【最新】<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/?refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2F%3Frefer%3DShare&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7OdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=87cd29ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2F%3Frefer%3DShare&h=1b16d13d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/?refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"ffae9128c2fe7d3f56281afe3365f32d9bda9c40","tid":1614182,"uid":2656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:14:25.000Z","msg":"到底係手足留手定點<br />\n次次都開得番嘅"},{"pid":"32d16efb49977c4dbba6398b42ed6d88db5fcde9","tid":1614182,"uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:15:15.000Z","msg":"度度有事第朝都用到<br />\n偏偏好少損壞既太子要兩日"},{"pid":"c34fe0c1d4e8e9b012c748c79642b18ac61f7d9a","tid":1614182,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:15:22.000Z","msg":"屌你次次第2朝咪照開，除左831"},{"pid":"f616d95f13dff008c6a9d0356f4a8847a5765b63","tid":1614182,"uid":62151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"